race.name: Coca-Cola 600
race.comments: Kyle Busch won the Monster Energy All-Star Race at Charlotte Motor Speedway, his first victory in the non-points event. Kyle Larson won Stage 1 and 2. Jimmie Johnson won Stage 3. Before the start of the event, no cars dropped to the rear of the field under penalty.
